item.title: End WA-7 South at US-12
item.description: End WA-7 south at US-12 East to White Pass/Yakima, and US-12 West to Mossyrock.

item.title: WA-7 North at WA-508 West to Onalaksa
item.description: WA-7 north to Mt. Ranier and Tacoma and WA-508 west to Onalaska.

item.title: Mt. Rainier NP Access on US-12 East at WA-7
item.description: US-12 east approaching WA-7 north. Use WA-7 for Mt. Rainer West Entrance. Continue on US-12 east for Mt. Rainier South Entrance.

item.description: US-12 east at WA-7 North/Morton/Mt. Ranier.
